author: @TheresaBryan-xp5mh
content: I saw Madonna 3 times in concert over 3 decades. This was really hard to watch. Lipsynced a lot of songs. Off key in others. Looks like she was a bit lost in coreography, very slow steps, off balance, no dancing at all, and she was famous for he dancing,  relied on characters too much. Yea..this should be her last tour, but if people are still willing to pay the bucks because they may have missed other tours good for them.
